overview: The LPL Spring Split Finals rematch gives BLG a 3rd chance this year to CHALLENGE expectations against JDG and becomes the #MSI2023 Champion. Regardless of the winner, the LPL became the first region ever to win the championship 3 times in a row in MSI history.
tagline: All roads lead to this match.
title: The 2023 Mid-Season Invitational Grand Finals (MSI 2023)
